nCorrespondence" target="L00671">Schnitzler an Hofmannsthal, 26. 4. 1897</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L00673">Hofmannsthal an Schnitzler, 2. 5. [1897]</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
